title: PawGo
author: PawGo
content: Because of critical issue in Profanity (Vanity address generator for Ethereum), many generated addresse have been hacked. The problem comes from very limited number of potential "search starting positions".If you generated your address using that tool - move your coins.More details: https://blog.1inch.io/a-vulnerability-disclosed-in-profanity-an-ethereum-vanity-address-tool-68ed7455fc8c
